                                        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                                        <h3>What is Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)?</h3>
                                        <p>AEO is the practice of structuring content so AI assistants like ChatGPT, Claude, Perplexity, Gemini and Google AI Overviews cite your site as the source when users ask questions. It is the natural successor to SEO for the AI-search era.</p>
                                        <h3>How is AEO different from SEO?</h3>
                                        <p>SEO targets ranking in Google's top-10 blue links and is measured by position, click-through and sessions. AEO targets being cited inside AI-generated answers and is measured by citation count, brand mention frequency and AI-referral traffic in GA4.</p>
